    95вҶ’## 2.2 State Management
    96вҶ’
    97вҶ’### 2.2.1 Library Overview
    98вҶ’
    99вҶ’**Package:** `@zazcart/tools` (located at `packages/toolkit`)
   100вҶ’
   101вҶ’The library provides a slice-based state machine pattern (NOT FSM/XState style) with:
   102вҶ’- Immer-powered immutable updates
   103вҶ’- React 18 `useSyncExternalStore` integration
   104вҶ’- Zero-allocation option for 60fps updates
   105вҶ’
   106вҶ’**Critical Note:** `@zazcart/tools` and `@belt/tools` are the SAME library (same GitHub repo, different npm names). No API migration required.
   107вҶ’
   108вҶ’### 2.2.2 createMachine Pattern
   109вҶ’
   110вҶ’The central state machine combines all slices:
   111вҶ’
   112вҶ’```typescript
   113вҶ’// File: apps/canvas/src/state/canvas-machine.ts
   114вҶ’import { createMachine } from '@zazcart/tools';
   115вҶ’import { viewportSlice } from './viewport';
   116вҶ’import { interactionSlice } from './interaction';
   117вҶ’
   118вҶ’export const canvasMachine = createMachine({
   119вҶ’  // Unique machine identifier
   120вҶ’  id: 'canvas',
   121вҶ’
   122вҶ’  // State slices to combine
   123вҶ’  slices: {
   124вҶ’    viewport: viewportSlice,
   125вҶ’    interaction: interactionSlice,
   126вҶ’  },
   127вҶ’
   128вҶ’  // Global context (shared across slices)
   129вҶ’  context: {
   130вҶ’    userID: null,  // Canvas is public/anonymous
   131вҶ’  },
   132вҶ’
   133вҶ’  // CRITICAL: Disable metadata tracking for 60fps
   134вҶ’  // Prevents per-dispatch object allocations that trigger GC
   135вҶ’  metadata: false,
   136вҶ’});
   137вҶ’
   138вҶ’// Typed React hooks
   139вҶ’export const useCanvas = canvasMachine.useMachine;
   140вҶ’export const useCanvasSelector = canvasMachine.useSelector;
   141вҶ’
   142вҶ’// Action creators (organized by slice)
   143вҶ’export const canvasActions = canvasMachine.actions;
   144вҶ’
   145вҶ’// Direct store access (for animation loops - NO React re-renders)
   146вҶ’export const canvasStore = {
   147вҶ’  getState: canvasMachine.getState,
   148вҶ’  dispatch: canvasMachine.dispatch,
   149вҶ’  subscribe: canvasMachine.subscribe,
   150вҶ’};
   151вҶ’```
