   154вҶ’
   155вҶ’Each state domain is a separate slice:
   156вҶ’
   157вҶ’```typescript
   158вҶ’// File: apps/canvas/src/state/viewport.ts
   159вҶ’import { createSyncSlice } from '@zazcart/tools';
   160вҶ’
   161вҶ’// Types
