  1277вҶ’## 2.6 Data Flow
  1278вҶ’
  1279вҶ’### 2.6.1 Data Generation Pipeline
  1280вҶ’
  1281вҶ’```
  1282вҶ’+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
  1283вҶ’|                      DATA GENERATION PIPELINE                      |
  1284вҶ’+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
  1285вҶ’
  1286вҶ’+------------------+     +------------------+     +------------------+
  1287вҶ’|                  |     |                  |     |                  |
  1288вҶ’|   Generator      | --> |   State Store    | --> |   Render Layer   |
  1289вҶ’|   (mock-data.ts) |     |   (canvasStore)  |     |   (LOD Layers)   |
  1290вҶ’|                  |     |                  |     |                  |
  1291вҶ’+--------+---------+     +--------+---------+     +--------+---------+
  1292вҶ’         |                        |                        |
  1293вҶ’         v                        v                        v
  1294вҶ’+------------------+     +------------------+     +------------------+
  1295вҶ’| Persistent Types |     | Runtime State    |     | GPU Buffers      |
  1296вҶ’|                  |     |                  |     |                  |
  1297вҶ’| - Train          |     | - ViewportState  |     | - InstanceMatrix |
  1298вҶ’| - Task           |     | - InteractionState|    | - InstanceColor  |
  1299вҶ’| - DatasetMeta    |     | - EntityStore    |     | - HTML overlays  |
  1300вҶ’+------------------+     +------------------+     +------------------+
  1301вҶ’```
  1302вҶ’
  1303вҶ’### 2.6.2 Type Flow: Persistent -> Render
  1304вҶ’
  1305вҶ’```typescript
  1306вҶ’// 1. Generator creates PERSISTENT data (serializable)
  1307вҶ’interface Task {
  1308вҶ’  id: string;
  1309вҶ’  trainId: string;
  1310вҶ’  startDate: string;      // ISO 8601: "2024-03-15"
  1311вҶ’  endDate: string;
  1312вҶ’  type: TaskType;
  1313вҶ’  hasConflict: boolean;
  1314вҶ’}
  1315вҶ’
  1316вҶ’// 2. Transform to RENDER data (calculated)
  1317вҶ’interface TaskRender {
  1318вҶ’  id: string;
  1319вҶ’  trainIndex: number;     // Calculated from trainId
  1320вҶ’  startDay: number;       // Days since meta.startDate
  1321вҶ’  duration: number;       // Days
  1322вҶ’  color: TaskColor;       // Derived from type
  1323вҶ’  hasConflict: boolean;
  1324вҶ’  type: TaskType;
  1325вҶ’}
  1326вҶ’
  1327вҶ’// 3. Transform function
  1328вҶ’function prepareRenderData(data: GeneratedData): TaskRender[] {
  1329вҶ’  const trainIndexMap = new Map(
  1330вҶ’    data.trains.map((t, i) => [t.id, i])
  1331вҶ’  );
  1332вҶ’  const startDate = new Date(data.meta.startDate);
  1333вҶ’
  1334вҶ’  return data.tasks.map(task => ({
  1335вҶ’    id: task.id,
  1336вҶ’    trainIndex: trainIndexMap.get(task.trainId)!,
  1337вҶ’    startDay: daysBetween(startDate, new Date(task.startDate)),
  1338вҶ’    duration: daysBetween(new Date(task.startDate), new Date(task.endDate)),
  1339вҶ’    color: TYPE_TO_COLOR[task.type],
  1340вҶ’    hasConflict: task.hasConflict,
  1341вҶ’    type: task.type,
  1342вҶ’  }));
  1343вҶ’}
  1344вҶ’```
  1345вҶ’
  1346вҶ’### 2.6.3 Viewport Culling Flow
  1347вҶ’
  1348вҶ’```
  1349вҶ’+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
  1350вҶ’|                      VIEWPORT CULLING FLOW                         |
  1351вҶ’+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
  1352вҶ’
  1353вҶ’1. User pans/zooms canvas
  1354вҶ’        |
  1355вҶ’        v
  1356вҶ’2. Camera position updates in state
  1357вҶ’        |
  1358вҶ’        v
  1359вҶ’3. Calculate viewport bounds in world coordinates:
  1360вҶ’
  1361вҶ’   viewportBounds = {
  1362вҶ’     minX: camera.x - (canvasWidth / 2) / zoom,
  1363вҶ’     maxX: camera.x + (canvasWidth / 2) / zoom,
  1364вҶ’     minY: camera.y - (canvasHeight / 2) / zoom,
  1365вҶ’     maxY: camera.y + (canvasHeight / 2) / zoom,
  1366вҶ’   }
  1367вҶ’        |
  1368вҶ’        v
  1369вҶ’4. Query RBush spatial index (O(log n + k)):
  1370вҶ’
  1371вҶ’   visibleTaskIds = spatialIndex.queryViewport(viewportBounds)
  1372вҶ’        |
  1373вҶ’        v
  1374вҶ’5. Map IDs to TaskRender objects:
  1375вҶ’
  1376вҶ’   visibleTasks = visibleTaskIds.map(id => taskMap.get(id))
  1377вҶ’        |
  1378вҶ’        v
  1379вҶ’6. Update InstancedMesh with visible tasks:
  1380вҶ’
  1381вҶ’   mesh.count = visibleTasks.length
  1382вҶ’   for (task, i) of visibleTasks:
  1383вҶ’     mesh.setMatrixAt(i, computeMatrix(task))
  1384вҶ’     mesh.setColorAt(i, computeColor(task))
  1385вҶ’   mesh.instanceMatrix.needsUpdate = true
  1386вҶ’```
  1387вҶ’
  1388вҶ’### 2.6.4 Interaction Data Flow
  1389вҶ’
  1390вҶ’```
  1391вҶ’+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
  1392вҶ’|                      INTERACTION DATA FLOW                         |
  1393вҶ’+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
  1394вҶ’
  1395вҶ’Mouse Move Event
  1396вҶ’        |
  1397вҶ’        v
  1398вҶ’Convert screen to world coordinates:
  1399вҶ’  worldX = (screenX - canvas.left) / zoom + camera.x - canvasWidth/2/zoom
  1400вҶ’  worldY = (screenY - canvas.top) / zoom + camera.y - canvasHeight/2/zoom
  1401вҶ’        |
  1402вҶ’        v
  1403вҶ’Query spatial index for nearest task:
  1404вҶ’  nearest = spatialIndex.queryNearest(worldX, worldY, maxDistance=50)
  1405вҶ’        |
  1406вҶ’        v
  1407вҶ’Dispatch interaction update:
  1408вҶ’  canvasStore.dispatch(canvasActions.interaction.setHoveredTask(nearest?.id))
  1409вҶ’        |
  1410вҶ’        v
  1411вҶ’MesoLayer useEffect triggers on hoveredTaskId change:
  1412вҶ’  - Recalculate colors for affected instances
  1413вҶ’  - Mark instanceColor.needsUpdate = true
  1414вҶ’```
  1415вҶ’
  1416вҶ’---
  1417вҶ’
  1418вҶ’## 2.7 Performance Monitoring
  1419вҶ’
  1420вҶ’### 2.7.1 Built-in Monitoring Components
  1421вҶ’
  1422вҶ’```typescript
  1423вҶ’// PerfMonitor - Custom performance panel
  1424вҶ’// File: apps/canvas/src/components/PerfMonitor.tsx
  1425вҶ’export function PerfMonitor() {
  1426вҶ’  const [stats, setStats] = useState({ fps: 0, frameTime: 0, memoryMB: 0 });
  1427вҶ’
  1428вҶ’  useFrame((_, delta) => {
  1429вҶ’    const fps = Math.round(1 / delta);
  1430вҶ’    const frameTime = delta * 1000;
  1431вҶ’    const memoryMB = (performance as any).memory?.usedJSHeapSize / 1024 / 1024;
  1432вҶ’
  1433вҶ’    setStats({ fps, frameTime, memoryMB });
  1434вҶ’  });
  1435вҶ’
  1436вҶ’  return (
  1437вҶ’    <div className="perf-monitor">
  1438вҶ’      <div>FPS: {stats.fps}</div>
  1439вҶ’      <div>Frame: {stats.frameTime.toFixed(1)}ms</div>
  1440вҶ’      <div>Memory: {stats.memoryMB.toFixed(1)}MB</div>
  1441вҶ’    </div>
  1442вҶ’  );
  1443вҶ’}
  1444вҶ’
  1445вҶ’// r3f-perf integration
  1446вҶ’import { Perf } from 'r3f-perf';
  1447вҶ’
  1448вҶ’<Canvas>
  1449вҶ’  {DEV_MODE && <Perf position="top-left" />}
  1450вҶ’</Canvas>
  1451вҶ’```
  1452вҶ’
  1453вҶ’### 2.7.2 Performance Checklist
  1454вҶ’
  1455вҶ’Before marking a feature complete:
  1456вҶ’
  1457вҶ’- [ ] 60fps during pan/zoom (use r3f-perf)
  1458вҶ’- [ ] No GC pauses > 10ms (use Chrome DevTools Performance)
  1459вҶ’- [ ] Viewport query < 1ms (use console.time)
  1460вҶ’- [ ] No memory leaks (stable memory over time)
  1461вҶ’- [ ] No console errors during demo flow
  1462вҶ’
  1463вҶ’---
  1464вҶ’
  1465вҶ’## 2.8 Summary: Architecture Decisions
  1466вҶ’
  1467вҶ’| Decision ID | Area | Choice | Rationale |
  1468вҶ’|-------------|------|--------|-----------|
  1469вҶ’| DECISION-007 | InstancedMesh | Pre-allocate 100k | Avoid GPU buffer reallocation |
  1470вҶ’| DECISION-008 | Viewport Query | RBush MANDATORY | O(log n) vs O(n) = 100x faster |
  1471вҶ’| DECISION-009 | GC Prevention | Object pooling | GC is primary bottleneck |
  1472вҶ’| DECISION-010 | MicroLayer | Max 50 labels | HTML is expensive |
  1473вҶ’| DECISION-011 | LOD Transition | depthWrite:false | Prevent z-fighting |
  1474вҶ’
  1475вҶ’### Technology Constraints (Magna Rules)
  1476вҶ’
  1477вҶ’| Rule | Constraint |
  1478вҶ’|------|------------|
  1479вҶ’| React | 18.3.1 (NOT 19) |
  1480вҶ’| R3F | 8.x (NOT 9.x) |
  1481вҶ’| drei | 9.x (NOT 10.x) |
  1482вҶ’| Three.js | 0.170.0 |
  1483вҶ’| State | @zazcart/tools with metadata:false |
  1484вҶ’| Queries | RBush (NEVER Array.filter for viewport) |
  1485вҶ’
