## 2.4 LOD System

### 2.4.1 Three-Layer Architecture

| Layer | Zoom Range | Visualization | Max Instances | Purpose |
|-------|------------|---------------|---------------|---------|
| **MACRO** | < 0.5x | Heatmap cells | 600 | 10-20 year strategic view |
| **MESO** | 0.5x - 2.0x | Task blocks | 100,000 (pre-alloc) | 2-5 year tactical view |
