+------------------+     +------------------+     +------------------+
|                  |     |                  |     |                  |
|   Generator      | --> |   State Store    | --> |   Render Layer   |
|   (mock-data.ts) |     |   (canvasStore)  |     |   (LOD Layers)   |
|                  |     |                  |     |                  |
+--------+---------+     +--------+---------+     +--------+---------+
         |                        |                        |
