+------------------+     +------------------+     +------------------+
| Persistent Types |     | Runtime State    |     | GPU Buffers      |
|                  |     |                  |     |                  |
| - Train          |     | - ViewportState  |     | - InstanceMatrix |
| - Task           |     | - InteractionState|    | - InstanceColor  |
| - DatasetMeta    |     | - EntityStore    |     | - HTML overlays  |
+------------------+     +------------------+     +------------------+
