```

### 2.6.4 Interaction Data Flow

```
+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                      INTERACTION DATA FLOW                         |
+-------------------------------------------------------------------+

Mouse Move Event
        |
        v
Convert screen to world coordinates:
  worldX = (screenX - canvas.left) / zoom + camera.x - canvasWidth/2/zoom
  worldY = (screenY - canvas.top) / zoom + camera.y - canvasHeight/2/zoom
        |
        v
Query spatial index for nearest task:
  nearest = spatialIndex.queryNearest(worldX, worldY, maxDistance=50)
        |
        v
Dispatch interaction update:
  canvasStore.dispatch(canvasActions.interaction.setHoveredTask(nearest?.id))
        |
        v
MesoLayer useEffect triggers on hoveredTaskId change:
  - Recalculate colors for affected instances
  - Mark instanceColor.needsUpdate = true
```

