## Appendix B: Glossary

### Railway Domain Terms

| Term | Definition |
|------|------------|
| **CBM** | Condition-Based Maintenance |
| **Dead Running** | Non-revenue movement of rolling stock |
| **Depot** | Designated maintenance facility |
| **ECM** | Entity in Charge of Maintenance (EU regulatory framework) |
| **Fleet** | Group of rolling stock sharing manufacturer/model |
| **Mileage Balancing** | Strategy to equalize wear across fleet |
| **RAMS** | Reliability, Availability, Maintainability, Safety |
| **Rolling Stock** | Railway vehicles requiring maintenance |
| **Run Assignment** | Daily allocation of train IDs to scheduled services |
| **Train Fitness** | Binary operational readiness (fit/unfit) |

### Maintenance Terms

| Term | Definition |
|------|------------|
| **HM** | Heavy Maintenance |
| **MDBF** | Mean Distance Between Failures |
| **MTBF** | Mean Time Between Failures |
| **MTTR** | Mean Time To Repair |
| **OVH** | Overhaul (resets counters) |
| **PM1/PM2/PM3** | Preventive Maintenance levels 1, 2, 3 |

### Technical Terms

| Term | Definition |
|------|------------|
| **CP** | Constraint Programming |
| **LOD** | Level of Detail |
| **MIP** | Mixed Integer Programming |
| **SoA** | Structure of Arrays (data layout) |

### MMS-Specific Terms

| Term | Definition |
|------|------------|
| **Blend Zone** | Zoom range where two LOD layers crossfade |
| **DNA Pattern** | Visual pattern of diagonal task stripes |
| **MACRO Layer** | Heatmap view at zoom < 0.5x |
| **MESO Layer** | Task block view at zoom 0.5x - 2.0x |
| **MICRO Layer** | Detailed card view at zoom > 2.0x |
| **Semantic Zoom** | Google Earth-style LOD switching |
| **TaskRender** | Computed task data for canvas rendering |

